summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 12240 entitled: "An ordinance regulating and relating to the construction and use of buildings for stables and repealing all ordinances or parts of ordinances in conflict herewith" approved March 29, 1905, and Ordinance No. 12791, approved September 8, 1905, and Ordinance No. 15479, approved February 25, 1907, and Ordinance No. 15723 approved April 8, 1907, amendatory thereof.
